A **salary hike** of 10–15% in CTC doesn't translate to the same percentage increase in take-home salary. The incremental income is taxed at your marginal slab rate, PF contributions increase, and professional tax remains flat — reducing the effective increase. This calculator shows your new take-home salary after a hike and the actual rupee benefit.
